Wikgit:  A Git-backed wiki

Goal: All functionality is available through Git as well as a browser.

Minimal Feature Set

* Spaces
* Versioning
* Directory support
* Users / Groups
* Wiki-based, space-based, page-based authz
* Automatic link rewriting
* Auto link generation
* orgmode support

Interacting with Git

* Installer can pick a git repo
  * New, installed with wikgit
  * New, already installed on a server
  ** New, Github
  ** Existing, installed as a directory
